        "product_description": {
            "value": "GEAR AID Tenacious Tape is the fast, reliable solution for fixing rips and holes in your favorite outdoor gear. This ultra-strong, peel-and-stick repair tape requires no heat or sewing, making repairs quick and easy wherever you are. Ideal for use on tents, tarps, puffy jackets, rain and snow gear, sleeping bags, vinyl furniture, and other synthetic materials. Its aggressive adhesive bonds permanently to nylon, mesh, vinyl, rubber, and plastic. Note that it is not recommended for use on seams, denim, cotton, or natural fabrics. Each repair is sealed with a waterproof coating that won't peel off over time, so you can wash your gear without worry. Available in a convenient 3”x20” strip that can be cut to the exact size and shape you need. Choose from nylon fabric options (black, red, yellow, OD green, and coyote), ripstop fabric (sage green and off-white), or clear vinyl for a nearly invisible repair. Trust GEAR AID Tenacious Tape to keep your equipment in top condition and extend the life of your gear on every adventure.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
            "model": "claude-opus-4-8"
